results.deck: Wizarbox is a French video game developer which specializes in providing services to other developers.
results.description:
Services Provided

The services this developer can provide include consulting, managing out-sourcing and in-sourcing needs as well as conversion, also known as 'porting'. The developer also offers these services in a number of other industries including architecture, defense, physics, and medical imaging.
